And the way we managed
to do that is people

00:14:45.780 --> 00:14:47.940
actually volunteered
to come in in tents

00:14:47.940 --> 00:14:49.770
and sleep in tents
in order to be

00:14:49.770 --> 00:14:52.080
able to increase the
amount of people.

00:14:52.080 --> 00:14:54.420
52, it's now going
to be 72 hours.

00:14:54.420 --> 00:14:56.430
40 useless projects.

