TentTech is taking
clean tech and doing

00:17:00.980 --> 00:17:02.690
that in the same
spirit of GeekCon.

00:17:02.690 --> 00:17:06.869
So in the desert, two
days, build things.

00:17:06.869 --> 00:17:08.480
But built in that space.

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:08.980
Right?

00:17:08.980 --> 00:17:12.640
It's not things that
you bring in advance.

00:17:12.640 --> 00:17:14.089
Well, OK.

00:17:14.089 --> 00:17:16.920
Amdocs, a company
that was doing this.

